quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  25,70,"Ikaŵeje ŵatesile toba, ni kulupilila, ni kupanganyaga masengo gambone; basi ŵanganyao Allah chakatindanichisye yakusakala yao ni yambone, soni Allah aŵele Jwakululuka kusyene, Jwachanasa channope."
  25,71,"Sano jwaakutenda toba ni kupanganyaga yambone, nikuti chisimu jwalakwejo jukulamba kwa Allah pakutenda toba jisyesyene."
  25,72,"Ni aŵala ŵangatendela umboni yaunami, nambo soni naga achipitaga malo ga yachanache akasapitaga mwa adabu (ja kuitundumalila yalakweyo)."
  26,43,"Musa jwasalile ŵanganyao kuti: “Ponyani jenumanja yankusaka kuponyayo.”"
  26,44,"Basi ni ŵaponyisye ngonji syao ni simbo syao, niŵatite: “Kwa machili ga Firiauna chisimu uwwe ni ŵachituŵe ŵakupunda.”"
  26,45,"Sano Musa ni jwaponyisye simbo jakwe. Naalole! Jalakwe jamisile mwanakamo yaunami yaŵaliji nkulosya."
  27,16,"Sano Sulaimana jwatamile chitengu cha Daudi. Ni jwatite: “E jenumanja ŵandu! Uwwe tujiganyisyidwe chiŵecheto cha ijuni, ni tupedwile chindu chilichose. Chisimu walakweu ni ukoto wakuonechela.”"
  27,17,"Ni ŵasonganganyisyidwe kwa Sulaimana asilikali ŵakwe kuumila m’majini, ŵandu ni ijuni. Basi ni ŵaliji ali nkwaalidwa m’mikutulamikutula (pakajende kakwe)."
  27,18,"Kwikanila ndema jaŵaiche ŵanganyao pachiŵata chambamba, lupamba lwatite (pakusisalila mbamba sijakwe): “E jenumanja achimbamba! Jinjilani m’majumba mwenu atakwika mwan’diŵete Sulaimana ni asilikali ŵakwe kutendaga ŵanganyao akakumanyilila.”"